com.mcc.ul
Class DaqDeviceConfig

java.lang.Object
  com.mcc.ul.DaqDeviceConfig

public class DaqDeviceConfig
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides methods to get or set configuration of a DAQ device. To create an instance of this class, call the getConfig() method of the DaqDevice class.
